. Dorsum (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1768,1790]" captionTargetBox="[175,1389,214,1672]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,195,1743]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Habitus and genitalia of Hantamsberg Hydraenidae. A) Mesoceration hantam sp. nov., holotype; B) Parhydraena faeni sp. nov., holotype; C) Mesoceration hantam sp. nov., aedeagus, ventral and lateral view; D) Parhydraena faeni sp. nov., aedeagus ventral and lateral views. Scale bar A – B = 1 mm; C – D = 0.25 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/252268/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="475">
